IN RE PROCTOR-BRISCOE, Minors. SC: 159464
COA: 345231 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 31, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 21, 2019 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
